dct_description_sm: These line file geodatabase feature classes represent bicycle lanes and bicycle routes for the City of Milwaukee, Wisconsin as of December, 2016. The file was obtained by the AGSL in early 2017. The layer includes the full City of Milwaukee DIME streets file with additional information about on-street bike infrastructure.
dct_creator_sm: City of Milwaukee Information and Technology Division - GIS Section
